176
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,039
I like listening to you.

177
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:47,200
Talk some more.

178
00:11:47,919 --> 00:11:48,679
Of course.

179
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:51,039
